= Git Subversion Tag

* http://github.com/hone/git_subversion_tag

== DESCRIPTION:

A tool I built to help maintain subversion tags based off of release branches

== REQUIREMENTS:

* git/git-svn > 1.6.x
needed for the git-svn branch/tag commands

== USAGE:

  ruby subversion_tag.rb <tag> <branch_name>

you must have the release branch already checked out and the tag must not already exist on SVN

